{"tid":1314172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田 即時地圖 測試版","createTime":"2019-07-14T05:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T06:28:53.000Z","uid":52105,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b8d4540dc3800b9d3608f55bd3d9c7b9091ce824","tid":1314172,"uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"[ 實時更新 Google Map 第一版 ]<br />\n<a href=\"https://pluvia-map.firebaseapp.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpluvia-map.firebaseapp.com&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPaoZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=e92dbfe9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pluvia-map.firebaseapp.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://pluvia-map.firebaseapp.com/maps/sha-tin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpluvia-map.firebaseapp.com%2Fmaps%2Fsha-tin&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPaoZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=a2659f84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pluvia-map.firebaseapp.com/maps/sha-tin</a><br />\n<br />\n是咁的一星期前我開post話要整個即時更新地圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1293568/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1293568/page/1</a><br />\n能力有限，但總叫有舊野玩下<br />\n呢個版本目的旨在做 Proof of Concept<br />\n去俾\b大眾感受即時更新地圖戰係咩野玩法<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Real-time</span></strong>係重點，所以user唔login都可以加 Marker<br />\nSecurity 我只係做左最低限度設定<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好信</span>地圖上面嘅Marker<br />\n<br />\n網頁有以下功能可以玩：<br />\n1. 主頁個Like制無限㩒，亦會即時更新其他人㩒<br />\n2. 地圖頁㩒落去會可以俾你加Marker，暫時只係揀左5個Marker玩<br />\n<del>3.</del> 只會顯示 last 100 Marker，因為唔想overload大家部手機<br />\n<br />\n已知問題：<br />\n- 手機版網頁移哂位，iPhone SE連個制都㩒唔到<br />\n<br />\n小弟真心覺得呢個網頁可以搞大佢<br />\n謹此跪求各位連登仔幫手做壓力測試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果反應好嘅話我會繼續寫落去 <br />\n<br />\nbetween, sorry for 1999<br />\n琴晚通左頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9afd565a77661c3cf376a0a29ddb3ff7e3f14304","tid":1314172,"uid":113680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T05:24:27.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9ee20c8dc3ee77a3737d404bb590c55a6e98de","tid":1314172,"uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T05:32:47.000Z","msg":"我想問開啱台有幾重要？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似開左係吹水台"},{"pid":"17ba017ba0ccea7d9ce91e090afc94ac75508f36","tid":1314172,"uid":7716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T05:34:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2550d1bffe7c8fdbe84acc9f2798daeb0ad8e145","tid":1314172,"uid":21340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T05:36:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b6548c71036cb392eac8c5baeee72e60a12bf111","tid":1314172,"uid":164646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T05:38:22.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但可唔可以講吓啲符代表啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21882d81948fd8de03f24dd4200a394b0a1f283c","tid":1314172,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T05:38:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【TVB唔驚我哋】啱啱有巴打打去置富 話答你唔到有無取消馬明2:00SHOW<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dipfkS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dipfkS</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">快啲出嚟！<br />\n<br />\n先紅磡後沙田！</span></span></strong><br />\n沙田起點係大圍站B出口！<br />\n日期： 14/7/2019<br />\n活動： 置富Malls‧OSARU NO MONKICHI『夏日狂熱運動會』開幕禮<br />\n嘉賓： 馬國明。<br />\n時間： 14:00<br />\n地點： 紅磡都會道6-10號<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">置富都會L7大堂</span></strong>"},{"pid":"bb81044aed116560ba9ba8a7353b9dbcaec842f8","tid":1314172,"uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T05:38:50.000Z","